snippet.title: Brant Carlson
snippet.description: This channel is a collection of physics video lectures recorded for or delivered at Carthage College.  As for me, I am a professor of physics at Carthage specializing in lightning and other forms of atmospheric electricity and high-energy atmospheric phenomena.
